title: Daurenbek Tazhimbetov
text:
Daurenbek Tazhimbetov (; born 2 July 1985 is a <a href="Kazakhs">Kazakh</a> <a href="association%20football">football</a> player who plays for <a href="FC%20Akzhayik">FC Akzhayik</a>.
Career.
In July 2013, Tazhimbetov joined <a href="FC%20Astana">FC Astana</a> on loan.
